Body: Whenever you're focus is on lead generation, it's important that your content addresses the customer pain points they're currently experiencing to grab their attention. Why should your target customer care about you? That's the story we need to tell across YouTube and LinkedIn.     Initially this will involve mapping your core value proposition to drive consistency across all customer touch points, online and offline. Content creation will come to life as details about the customer problems you solve rise to the surface.
